  "loadout": "<b>This model is equipped with:</b> Terrax melta cutter; 2 combi-bolters; Termite drill.",
  "transport": "This model has a transport capacity of 12 <span class=\"tooltip00317\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00317\" data-tooltip-anchor=\"#tooltip_content00317\"><span class=\"kwb\">HERETIC</span> <span class=\"kwb\">ASTARTES</span> <span class=\"kwb\">INFANTRY</span></span> models. It cannot transport <span class=\"tooltip00319\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00319\" data-tooltip-anchor=\"#tooltip_content00319\"><span class=\"kwb\">JUMP</span> <span class=\"kwb\">PACK</span></span>, <span class=\"tooltip\" title=\"Keyword does not appear in that faction.\"><s class=\"kwbs\">WULFEN</s></span>, <span class=\"tooltip\" title=\"Keyword does not appear in that faction.\"><s class=\"kwbs\">PHOBOS</s></span>, <span class=\"tooltip\" title=\"Keyword does not appear in that faction.\"><s class=\"kwbs\">GRAVIS</s></span>, <span class=\"tooltip\" title=\"Keyword does not appear in that faction.\"><s class=\"kwbs\">CENTURION</s></span>, <span class=\"tooltip00318\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00318\" data-tooltip-anchor=\"#tooltip_content00318\"><span class=\"kwb\">TERMINATOR</span></span>, <span class=\"kwb kwbo\">OBLITERATOR</span>, <span class=\"kwb kwbo\">POSSESSED</span> or <span class=\"tooltip\" title=\"Keyword does not appear in that faction.\"><s class=\"kwbs\">TACTICUS</s></span> models (excluding <span class=\"kwb\">TACTICUS</span> <span class=\"kwb\">CHARACTER</span> models that began the battle attached to a non-<span class=\"kwb\">TACTICUS</span> unit).",
